Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:29.75,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:34.86,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard about\NYoshiko's Christmas event?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:36.94,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:41.13,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshiko's having a party at\Nher apartment on Christmas Eve!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:42.86,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,There's supposed to be\Na lot of fine guys there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:44.38,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname, you come too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.51,0:00:47.39,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll have to decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:48.91,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:51.81,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you've already got\Na date with some guy on that night!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.58,0:00:57.26,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that... could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.14,0:01:54.30,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that your sister's\Nhomecoming will be on Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.48,0:02:01.07,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Amemiya, about Christmas Eve...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.61,0:02:35.24,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,My soul is hers alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:19.80,georgia 36pts,,0290,0000,0060,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,6000,9830,9460)}{\fs18}{\c&H8D6368&}{\3c&HF8DBDF&}Chapter  Three
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:19.80,georgia 36pts,,0000,0290,0040,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,6000,9830,9460)}{\fs18}#LAMONAE @ RIZON presents...\NRipping etc. by Robink\NScript meddling by ics-\NSpecial thanks: CharlieB & kurochocho
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:23.68,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! This winter break is\Nfull of fun events!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:27.54,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you have to come to\Nthe Christmas party, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:29.72,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening, Kaname?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:34.86,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, "Come to the party\Non Christmas Eve", is what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:38.37,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:40.77,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you already\Nhave something planned?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:45.34,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Like meeting up with Amemiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.11,0:04:49.24,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,So the rumors were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:54.61,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't really trying\Nto hide anything, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:57.93,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname, do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:07.63,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you spending\NChristmas Eve night with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:11.41,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:14.31,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're thinking,\N"Maybe there's a chance."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:18.71,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname, I think you already know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:22.01,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,...he's not the kind of person who\Ncan understand your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:25.12,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how long you wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:27.59,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,...there's no way he's ever\Ngoing to say, "I love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:30.13,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that still okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:33.49,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:35.73,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You're seriously in love with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:37.86,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:42.28,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname, you're so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:44.26,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:04.78,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:06.36,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:09.52,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally tomorrow, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:10.44,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:13.26,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Narita Airport, 4:00pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:15.23,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:18.43,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds as though it'll be\Na wonderful Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:32.18,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:35.59,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:39.99,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:43.89,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,...I so want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:49.66,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:52.43,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Amemiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:55.20,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kaname.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:07:02.21,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I want to see you\Ntomorrow, on Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:05.11,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,See me and then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:08.01,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay if you'll just see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:13.29,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It's enough if you'll just be with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:15.42,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:22.73,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:03.27,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,In a little while, she'll call my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:08.21,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:08.91,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:18.13,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:26.91,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.09,0:09:30.15,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:32.06,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:35.46,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,...Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:50.68,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally get to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:55.32,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't forgotten you,\Nnot even for a day, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:57.75,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me get a good look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:09:58.89,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:03.16,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is your beloved brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:10.20,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes sense. He is as\Ncute as you've always bragged he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:16.90,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my makeup artist and personal\Nassistant from abroad, Chihaya Aso.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:19.05,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.46,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, should I buy\Nsome wine glasses, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:47.13,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:50.10,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:54.01,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you are alone today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:58.35,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on over to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:09.69,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.26,0:11:14.17,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,That cameraman back then,\Nwhat was his name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:15.57,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it Louis?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:16.74,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:20.10,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,The way he acted, he'd go after\Nanything female, even a dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:21.07,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:24.38,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,He put his hands on my hips!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:25.90,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, wasn't that an honor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:30.23,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he is the number one\Nfashion photographer in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:33.84,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I have a right to choose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.47,0:11:52.37,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all just the\Nsame as the day I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:54.77,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for you, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:56.52,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:02.01,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, those flowers.\NAre they for me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:04.75,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. They are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:09.72,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I want to start on dinner, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:12.19,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya, I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:15.47,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira, you can just relax, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.10,0:12:19.00,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:29.50,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hanging out here is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:31.33,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it is Christmas...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:32.84,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,...so let's go somewhere together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:36.14,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, aren't you a bit depressing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:36.94,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:40.54,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You're thinking it'd have been better\Nif you hadn't come, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:42.05,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:44.65,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, don't just sit there and mope!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:52.36,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname, I know it might not be possible\Nto not think about him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:53.66,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:56.16,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?\NThen we have to liven things up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:12:57.74,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it's Christmas Eve!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.37,0:13:00.77,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, that guy and\Nthat one are free, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:04.07,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,And then this one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:09.21,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,This Italian transvestite makeup\Nguy was weird, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:13.10,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't he the one who used the\Nsame compliments on every model?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:14.82,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:19.66,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,And this transvestite was doing\Nit because it was his job...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:22.10,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,...but he said it\Nwas definitely more fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:24.93,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,...to put makeup on\Nhimself than on the models.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:26.47,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:27.93,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,But with that face...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:30.66,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,...it made no difference\Nwhether he did or not, did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:36.41,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, Akira is so\Nbeautiful, I'm sure if we made him up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:38.92,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,...it'd turn out great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:44.04,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't we make up Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:48.85,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Akira, why don't you\Nhave her do it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:52.25,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Your skin's so beautiful, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:53.76,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure to look good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:55.26,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I don't want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.63,0:14:02.10,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister would like to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:04.00,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll show me, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:06.16,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:07.60,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:15.71,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:20.85,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our special secret, just\Nbetween you and me, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:23.09,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:45.15,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Akira, you're so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:51.62,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he's this beautiful, it makes\Nyou want to dress him up, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:54.74,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, what about your promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:03.06,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira, why don't you try this on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:05.07,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:13.97,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:15.74,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:16.73,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:18.64,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:34.02,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:38.91,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You look wonderful, Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:42.87,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,If you said that you were a girl now,\Npeople would believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:46.36,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you use that wig over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:48.20,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be even more surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:51.91,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:01.64,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.67,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You look exactly like your sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:06.68,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You're stunning, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:09.63,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:13.12,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you break your promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:15.80,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.41,0:16:25.44,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:31.74,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up! Akira, open it, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:34.97,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:39.33,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister, the only one you love is yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:50.46,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you don't love anyone else,\Nit doesn't bother you to hurt others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:51.76,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:56.93,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I've loved you all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:03.21,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:08.95,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira, stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:12.86,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.04,0:17:58.33,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.82,0:18:03.77,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,She was seeing herself in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:07.47,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw perfection in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.95,0:18:13.39,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,She's unrestrained and selfish,\Nand she casually hurts people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:18.02,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,But, she's more\Nbeautiful than anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:22.33,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.32,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Amemiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:18:58.42,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Amemiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:36.16,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I got to see you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.54,0:19:40.97,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.67,0:19:44.77,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Just being with you is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:55.05,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me by my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:20:01.19,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,My name. Call me "Akira".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:12.64,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, look only at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:26.28,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:28.75,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,...I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:39.79,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:44.73,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}{\i1}You are waiting for...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:48.03,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}{\i1}... something to begin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:50.90,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}{\i1}Standing in the dark...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:55.61,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}{\i1}... like a scene that's{\i0}\N{\i1}waiting for the rain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:20:59.47,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}{\i1}You just don't know...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:03.69,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}{\i1}... what you want to do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:07.96,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}{\i1}Have you ever thought...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:11.42,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}{\i1}... I might be your dream?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:16.83,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}{\i1}I will be sweet all the time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:20.77,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}{\i1}I'll be very sweet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:22.87,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}{\i1}... always and just right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:28.88,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}{\i1}Just right are we two.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:34.78,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}{\i1}You're the only{\i0}\N{\i1}one who makes me feel that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:35.93,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:40.72,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}{\i1}... there is nothing to be afraid of.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.49,0:21:46.43,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}{\i1}You're the only one{\i0}\N{\i1}who makes me feel that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:52.36,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}{\i1}... here in this{\i0}\N{\i1}world I was born to love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:57.77,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}{\i1}I believe in you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.68,0:22:03.84,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}{\i1}You don't have{\i0}\N{\i1}to be waiting anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.58,0:22:08.49,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}{\i1}Did you know you can start it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.19,0:22:15.68,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}{\i1}When you find what you{\i0}\N{\i1}really want to do someday...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.50,0:22:23.06,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}{\i1}... you will find a way, surely you will.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.14,0:22:25.16,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,So good...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.06,0:22:45.05,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.43,0:22:51.56,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.04,0:23:08.24,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}You're the only one\Nwho makes me feel that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.85,0:23:13.95,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}...there is nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.69,0:23:19.89,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}You're the only one\Nwho makes me feel that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.59,0:23:25.76,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}...here in this\Nworld I was born to love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.60,0:23:31.87,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.87,0:23:40.01,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}You don't have\Nto be waiting anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.65,0:23:44.58,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}...'cuz you know you can start it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:51.75,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}When you find what you\Nreally want to do someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.66,0:23:59.53,Arabolical 28,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H10d060&}...you will find a way,\Nsurely you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.77,0:24:09.80,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira...
